---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — ReviewBoard" description="Learn more about ReviewBoard and our review process.">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About ReviewBoard</h1>
    <p>We're a team of product testers and researchers dedicated to helping you make better buying decisions. Every product we review is tested in real-world conditions for at least two weeks.</p>

    <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Research</strong> — We analyze specs, read user feedback, and identify key testing criteria.</li>
      <li><strong>Real-World Testing</strong> — Every product is used in daily scenarios for 14+ days.</li>
      <li><strong>Scoring</strong> — We rate each product on performance, build quality, value, and user experience.</li>
      <li><strong>Publishing</strong> — We write honest reviews with clear pros, cons, and verdicts.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Why Trust Us?</h2>
    <p>We never accept payment for positive reviews. Our affiliate links help fund our work, but they never influence our opinions. If a product sucks, we'll tell you.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
